{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-ST-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "旅行前夕", "storyInfo": "身在羅德島的嘉維爾和森蚺收到了回家休假的特米米留下的信，據說來自地下的杜林人帶來了整片雨林都處在危險之中的消息。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smithy", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "叮噹、叮噹。真是忙碌啊，阿卡胡拉人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你問我們在做什麼？哈，阿卡胡拉的戰士們還能做什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "最偉大的武器，強大的造物，有了大祭司與依娜姆商會的協助，我們可以輕鬆創造更多的器械！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "征服！“貢業”！阿卡胡拉的名號將會響徹雲霄！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_village_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " “貢業”，“貢業”，啊，這個詞真是太美好了......是這麼發音的吧，尤吉？", "name": "激動的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，哥哥。是“工業”。而且，你應該注意休息。而不是跑來攪和......呃，全自動種植砍伐一體化機器人“叢林三號”的作業。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準確來說經過昨晚的報廢和重修，現在已經是四號了。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤吉，我最近狀態好得很，不用擔心。真沒想到，石頭......哦，源石還能這麼用，真是讓人大開眼界！是新的技術？誰搞來的？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多半是依娜姆。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......如同嘉維爾一般的怪力，又可以將上半身螺旋發射，甚至還能滯留在空中半分鐘之久......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，確實很驚人，不過大祭司將那玩意當時的狀態稱之為“解體”。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前就在想了，尤吉。你看，外面的大地如此廣闊，我們現在有了這麼多的......“汞業”！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工業。而且這個詞不是這麼用的，大祭司說過。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那無所謂，更重要的是越來越多的巨大機械！還有越來越簡單的操作，越來越低的事故機率！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我們是不是可以做更多事情？！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......比如？", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有點野心，弟弟，把目光放向整個薩爾貢，你想像到了嗎——", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，喔......", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我們的雕像！有三座山那麼高！有兩片湖那麼大！！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔哦哦——！", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了，族長的雕像也得有......還有大祭司的！依娜姆的也不能落下......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，還需要一些紀念性質的......建築！對！宮殿！我想想......用木頭？不行，得是砂岩或者堅硬的石頭......乾脆用源石！對！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用源石塊堆起來！堆一個巨大的建築！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "堆起來？什、什麼形狀？和那些神殿一樣？", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是簡單一些好，比如圓形......唔，石頭堆不出圓形。那就逐層向上，從每個方向看都是三角形！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦......哦！三角！塔！剩下的只有取名了啊！", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不過，說這些也沒用了啊。嘉維爾說過，我這種病是看不到那一天的......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥哥......不！我們只要改變一下思維，把宮殿變成哥哥的墳墓不就好了嗎？", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這下別說阿卡胡拉了，整個薩爾貢都不會忘記哥哥的，名字也有了，就叫“尤吉尤塔塔”！我們一定會在哥哥有生之年建完那座塔！", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤吉......！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要說這麼不吉利的話啦......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，特米米......你怎麼還在這呢？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為昨天你就一刻不停地跑回去找嘉維爾和族長啦。", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難得有機會回來看一看，我總不能那麼快就走吧？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是。所以你今天來這裡做什麼？已經來打過招呼了吧？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "刻薄的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，你是依娜姆提過的那個小個子。怎麼，難道是來抱怨今天的伙食的？哎呀，我也覺得最近的飲食太清淡了點，沒肉怎麼行......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，別的事。還有，我是斯第奇·畫布。別只看著別人的身高，阿達克利斯人都是這樣嗎？", "name": "刻薄的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#4"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，其實不是這樣的......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#4"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，畢竟是一幫為了尾巴粗細就能吵起架來的奇怪傢伙......我應當尊重這種文化差異。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#2"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸、欸......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#2"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，斯第奇，你有什麼事嗎？我們正在規劃薩爾貢的宏偉“藍禿”。", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍圖。", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，對。藍圖，你聽見了嗎，杜林人。這可真是個偉大計畫！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得......一座誇張的大墳墓應該不算什麼偉大計畫......而且如果大家都有那麼大的墳墓，這座雨林就裝不下啦。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別總是當做墳墓，就是紀念，紀念性質！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建造得大一點，我也可以和族長和嘉維爾放在一起吧，後世會抱著孩子們在我們幾人的雕像前講述祖瑪瑪與“嘉維爾意志”的美談......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我開始懷疑我的決定了......）", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！但、但是......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，眼下我們不該——", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——但是這樣就不能叫“尤吉尤塔塔”了！嘉維爾必須出現在名字裡！我、我也可以順便......！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不是......是這樣，依娜姆和斯第奇先生好好聊過了，我打算讓大家都聽聽他說的事情。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟事關重大，我也留了給嘉維爾的信，不知道她們能不能趕到......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事？什麼事？我可是在給自己所剩無幾的人生規劃結尾！難道還能比這件事更重要嗎？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......咳。我無意對各位地上人的奇思妙想發表意見，只是......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我之前說的那樣，如果我們的城市真的遭遇了危機，災難會摧毀一切。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，再宏偉的奇觀，也不過只是一堆瓦礫罷了吧。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，祖瑪瑪。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......嘉維爾啊，我們居然是同時回來的。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？那些感染者安穩下來了嗎？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你以為我是誰？不光那些感染者，礦場的保安、附近的農民，包括那個雷姆必拓的老東西，我全都擺平了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老東西......你把合夥人一起擺平了？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，他對待感染者的方式也有些小問題，我自然要和藹地從醫生的角度提些意見。“從醫生的角度，用嘉維爾的方式”。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不提這些了，你看見信了嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒回宿舍......特米米的信？我記得她回家探親了來著。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#3", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在這之前她也一直透過依娜姆和阿卡胡拉的朋友們聯繫著呢。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#3"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#3", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過，在她出發的時候，似乎本來是打算叫上我們一起的。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#3"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#3", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一起嗎......可露希爾師父沒給我安排什麼工作的話，回去看看也不錯。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#3", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，如果只是這種事情，嘉維爾你是不會來找我的吧。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 幹嘛，我們平時有很生分嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了。所以，依娜姆說了什麼？特米米遇上麻煩了？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，準確來說，是整片雨林都遇上麻煩了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_187_ccheal_1#5", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 準備一下吧，我們可是有一場大冒險了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_187_ccheal_1#5"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_village_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 整、整片雨林會沉入地下？！地貌會發生劇烈變化？！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林族的城市結構......說了你們也不明白。總之，這片雨林不遠處的地底，就是我所在的城市。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我們遇上了點麻煩......所以我才向地上人求助。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來我對你們是不抱太大希望的，但我看到了你們在做的事情。也許你們能幫上忙。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽上去是大問題啊......但是和我們部族沒什麼關係吧？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可是，按照這個傢伙說的，如果那座杜林城市毀滅了，造成的連鎖反應一定會影響到地上......那我們的尤吉尤塔塔......", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反過來說，如果你們幫了我們，憑藉杜林人的科技，也許我們可以回報你們。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#9$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不知道你們的科學發展軌跡......不過看得出，你們偶爾也原始得離譜。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫忙？外族人嗎？這我可說不準......", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，要說外族......地上人不也是......沒什麼。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，斯第奇先生指點改造“叢林三號”時確實一針見血地找到了問題，雖說好像削減了大量的功能......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靠他？！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，所以依娜姆出於各種考慮......決定陪斯第奇先生下去看看。我、我當然也會跟著，作為“嘉維爾意志”的族長。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#5"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，就得靠你們照顧提亞卡烏的大家啦。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒是沒問題......不如說，為了我們的尤......不對，是“偉大阿卡胡拉赤金源石翡翠偉大三角塔”，你們可一定要順利解決問題啊！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......偉大用了兩次。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#3"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會的。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#3"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你們要怎麼去那裡......我們連離開這片叢林的次數都不多吧，真不會迷路嗎？", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為有我在。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#2"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極、極境先生！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#2"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是那個羅德島的......", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強韌如我也不得不靠假期旅行來排解作戰時累積的壓力，結果卻捲入了另一場拯救杜林人大作戰......算了，好像挺有趣的。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少迪倫和煌都沒說錯，這是個既能不讓自己閒下來，又能稍微放鬆一下的好地方。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#4"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過傳言中那種美味的蘑菇，我可是翻遍了叢林都沒找到啊......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#4"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#4"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望依娜姆小姐可以信守承諾，到時候幫我完成“來到阿卡胡拉必須完成的七件事”吧。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#4"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境先生已經和斯第奇先生初步交流過了，有他們二位做嚮導，我們是不會迷路的......他們這麼保證的。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "char_411_tomimi_1#1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，恐怕等不到嘉維爾和森蚺回家，我們就能把事情全部擺平啦。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "showall", "image": "bg_corridor", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明以前性子最急的是她，現在我卻要在走廊上等她半個小時嗎......", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這套新裝備......我還以為嘉維爾每個月都會提一次這樣的申請，從可露希爾師父的反應來看，並非如此啊。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是不打算再以“逃離部族學醫”的身份回去的意思嗎。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這也太久了！嘉維爾，你到底在做什麼？！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別催啦！你們弄的這套裝備為什麼這麼複雜？！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處理緊急訂單的極限就是如此了，要抱怨的話，下次老老實實從工程部那裡走流程。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好——麻煩！卡西米爾的騎士都不會穿這麼多礙事的盔甲！！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，你有什麼不明白的地方——", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 100.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_debut", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "power": 20.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不管了！就這樣吧，剩下的都不要了！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#4$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那些剩下的亂七八糟的玩意我全都丟在裡面啦，不需要。當我握上這把斧頭的時候就已經全明白了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......明白什麼？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#6"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我有這傢伙就夠了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你做的？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處理緊急訂單。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 果然，這麼棒的傢伙只有你做得出來。從平衡性到重量都無可挑剔。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過這個小掛飾......", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大姐說過，要對自己經手的東西傾注感情，無論是病人還是裝備。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " Lancet-2還會說這種話啊，大概是可露希爾教的，隨便你們吧。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那麼，我們出發！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘉維爾！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 幹嘛，這次輪到你在拖了？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算......怎麼做？特米米收到了杜林人的求援，聽上去是一次關乎他們城市的危機。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是天災......或者是戰爭。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 雖然信裡描述的“火焰從天上掉下來把所有人的被子都燒掉”和“巨大的蘑菇撐破地面遮天蔽日導致植物無法生長”都太抽象了......", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過不管是什麼麻煩，我們都有辦法解決吧。不是還有依娜姆和極境嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼解決？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你不是才把答案送我嗎？看看這身行頭，祖瑪瑪，說真的，我現在久違地有些亢奮。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是，拳頭說了算。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈，老樣子！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......老樣子啊......", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 時間不等人，祖瑪瑪。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 難道不想看一眼你族裡那些傢伙，把叢林變成了什麼樣嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呵呵，說得對。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出發吧。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}